      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "0b5aa6d808358fd1",
      "text": "Let's say you are running [[Node.js]] on a remote machine, remote.example.com, that you want to be able to debug. On that machine, you should start the node process with the inspector listening only to localhost (the default)."
    },
